query:
UPDATE station SET 
        gr_id = COALESCE($2, gr_id),
        typ = (SELECT id FROM stationstyp WHERE value = $3),
        titel = COALESCE($4, titel),
        zp_start = $5, zp_modifiziert = COALESCE($6, NOW()),
        trojanergefahr = COALESCE($7, trojanergefahr),
        link = COALESCE($8, link),
        gremium_isff = $9
        WHERE station.id = $1
